text: Money in the Bank (2015) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view and livestreaming show made by WWE. It took place on June 14, 2015 at the Nationwide Arena in Columbus, Ohio. It was the sixth Money in the Bank event held by WWE. ==Matches== == References == == Other websites == * WWE Money in the Bank Category:2010s in Ohio Category:Sports in Ohio Category:2015 in American television Category:2015 in professional wrestling
